//!
//! Project: baton (cli)
//! AC description: `baton peers` reads ~/.cache/baton/surfaces/*.json and emits a JSON array; missing dir is non-fatal (empty array).
//! Test predicate: tests/acceptance_ac2.rs
//!
//! Ownership split: this //! header block (AC metadata) is
//! read-only — to change an AC, file
//! agent/intent_card_amendment_request.json and re-scaffold. The
//! `fn acceptance_ac2` body BELOW is owned by the edit-agent: replace
//! the panic stub with a real assertion that verifies the AC
